items.title: Phils claim lefty Curtis off waivers
items.summary: The Phillies added bullpen depth Monday when they claimed left-hander Zac Curtis off waivers from the Mariners. Curtis, 25, allowed three unearned runs in 4 2/3 innings in three appearances this season with Seattle.
